### Login como cliente
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "client@example.com",
  "password": "Senha@123"
}

###
### Criar conversa como cliente
POST http://localhost:3000/chat/conversations
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{client_access_token}}

{
  "clientId": "cmp_client_id",
  "realtorId": "cmp_realtor_id",
  "propertyId": "cmp_property_id",
  "initialMessage": "Olá! Tenho interesse neste imóvel e queria tirar algumas dúvidas."
}

###
### Listar minhas conversas
GET http://localhost:3000/chat/conversations
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{client_access_token}}

###
### Buscar uma conversa específica
GET http://localhost:3000/chat/conversations/cmp_conversation_id
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{client_access_token}}

###
### Arquivar conversa
PATCH http://localhost:3000/chat/conversations/cmp_conversation_id/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{client_access_token}}

{
  "status": "ARCHIVED"
}

###
### Reabrir conversa
PATCH http://localhost:3000/chat/conversations/cmp_conversation_id/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{client_access_token}}

{
  "status": "OPEN"
}

###
### Enviar mensagem
POST http://localhost:3000/chat/messages
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{client_access_token}}

{
  "conversationId": "cmp_conversation_id",
  "content": "Conseguimos agendar uma visita para esta semana?"
}

###
### Listar mensagens da conversa
GET http://localhost:3000/chat/messages?conversationId=cmp_conversation_id
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{client_access_token}}

###
### Listar mensagens não lidas
GET http://localhost:3000/chat/messages?conversationId=cmp_conversation_id&unreadOnly=true
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{client_access_token}}

###
### Marcar mensagem como lida
PATCH http://localhost:3000/chat/messages/read
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{client_access_token}}

{
  "messageId": "cmp_message_id"
}
